metadata.name: Birthstone Series #01 "Garnet"
metadata.description:
This is the first of a series of twelve pieces in the "Birthstone Series".

Garnet the birthstone for January is said to symbolize fruitfulness and has meanings such as "deepening bonds between people", "enriching the heart", "bringing to fruition hard work", "strengthening the spirit" and "inspiring courage and passion". I drew this illustration to express the power of garnet.

I hope this NFT will bring you happiness.
